        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-cta-content">
                <h2>Join Our Journey</h2>
                <p>Become part of the IndiaKart family and experience premium shopping like never before</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/products" class="btn btn-light">
